   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1910_AS_RBH_1_00016"/>Hrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb68" type="place">Wien XVIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb235251">Hasenauerstr 59</rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1910_AS_RBH_1_00017"/><salute>lieber Richard,</salute><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01939-1"/><date>Montag</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01939-1"><ref target="1910-06-27" subtype="See" type="schnitzler-tagebuch"/>.
               </note><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>Abend</time><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb29937"><hi rend="latintype">Medardus</hi></rs> Conferenz im <rs ref="#pmb14" type="place">Burgth</rs>; –<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o muß ich die
               <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01939-2"/><rs type="event" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb48222">Vorle<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>g</rs> auf 
               <date>Mittwoch 29.</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01939-2"><ref target="pmb48222" subtype="Cf" type="schnitzler-kultur"/>. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann</rs>
                  nahm nicht teil.
               </note><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>Abends ½ 7</time> ver<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chieben (<date>Din<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date> unmöglich) – werden Sie
               noch da<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ein? Ich hoffe!</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<lb/><signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
